.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43cf9874629e01ff944b2e9530cf94a7a6ea9db","tid":2137380,"uid":281054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:22:57.000Z","msg":"都係做戲，扯貓尾一唱一和"},{"pid":"91cc3be7d99eb5f24087f438728816f653920ace","tid":2137380,"uid":281054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:23:46.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>割地！？</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05446c20fbacf2127dcd440239ac131bb4550611","tid":2137380,"uid":57480,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:24:13.000Z","msg":"痴L線，大家等入集中營"},{"pid":"d8000ffe004c254077e14b3bfe3364ec2e5834ee","tid":2137380,"uid":65074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:24:19.000Z","msg":"整完實驗室又派幾百人黎<br />\n打個風冇左個實驗室再起過<br />\ncap水gogogo"},{"pid":"78e759249b11594ab51539edc58731027a7b56bd","tid":2137380,"uid":54337,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f8447ecb7e1dcf1f640f10b213de4e96e2f44bce","tid":2137380,"uid":121197,"like":71,"dislike":3,"score":68,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T01:53:42.000Z","msg":"拉晒啲本地專家咪得囉<br />\n咁就可以全民檢測"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:24:34.000Z","msg":"奧運完左之後，個雙魚河馬術中心一直養老鼠，張塊地變埋左醫院囉"},{"pid":"803eefdb8316a3e9ea8bd4193513a97dffd89cb0","tid":2137380,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:26:53.000Z","msg":"整下又多舊<br />\n整下又多舊<br />\n每日150個咪就係咁"},{"pid":"669d333a4d1a794cd964a3950dde32ddb8d7589a","tid":2137380,"uid":35315,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T02:26:56.000Z","msg":"梗係唔撚推啦<br />\n一定過萬人中左招<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac